power-installer (0.2) trusty; urgency=low

    * Added new option for installing plank themes (elementary OS)
    * Improved interface
    * New types of notifications
    * Bug fixes:
    - script files got created in unexpected directories
    - the commands weren't accepted due to the bad implementation of confirm system
    - some optimalizations in the code (general.sh)
    - when user commands were executed Power Installer window wasn't responding
    - massive code clean
    - the application now removes the "lock" files to execute all user commands

 -- Adam Bieńkowski <donadigos159@gmail.com>  Sat, 15 Nov 2014 18:00:00 -0500

power-installer (0.3) trusty; urgency=low

    * API detects if application was installed
    * Huge code cleaning
    * Bug fixes:
    - tar.gz and tar.bz2 files weren't unpacked
    - now Power Installer window scales normal
    - improved executing user commands
    - optimalizations in the vala code

 -- Adam Bieńkowski <donadigos159@gmail.com>  Sat, 22 Nov 2014 18:00:00 -0500

power-installer (0.4) trusty; urgency=low

    * Bash to python transformation
    * Now using policy-kit
    * Overall optimalization
    * Added "no_display" key to API to not show APP_NAME, CATEGORY and SUBTITLE
    * Bug fixes:
    - first argument was passed as a file
    - typo fixes
    - TERM variable is not exported so the commands failed
    - removed unsecure password system

